      <section name="Download Validator">
         
         <subsection name="Releases">
            <p>Download the <a href="http://jakarta.apache.org/site/downloads/downloads_commons-validator.cgi">Latest Release</a>
               of Commons Validator.
            </p>
            <p>For details of whats new in each version see the <a href="changes-report.html">Release History</a>.</p>
